                           <p>Fragments of fresco on <objectType>wall plaster</objectType>. The original design appears to have been a series of circular garlands of green leaves, outlined inside and outside with a sold band; The fragments come from at least three such garlands; fragment iv may well come from the same text as fragment iii.</p>
                        </support>
